name: PULSR
description: The project is about creating a token, that allows people to buy products created by the company PULSR. PULSR is a top web 2 AI company in the field of GPT development. With $PULSR you will get access to private GPTs never released to public, and also new products developed specifically for web 3 such as the Overseer. The Overseer is a layer that will allow communities to build their own AI Agents, creating more engagement with their members.
